=============
R Cheat Sheet
=============

Getting Help
------------
help(c)  -->  Get help on 'c'
?c


View Examples
-------------
example(c)  -->  View example of 'c'


Search for Help on a Topic
--------------------------
help.search("regression")  -->  Search for help on 'regression'
??regression


Help on Specific Library
------------------------
library(help="tm")  -->  Get help on 'tm' library


Access Package Vignette
-----------------------
vignette("tm")  -->  Access tm's vignette


